creator: Appus Studio
descriptionHtml:
Boost your Instagram account by getting more likes on your posts for free. It's simple!
You will be exchanging likes with other users of the app and you will get to choose which posts to like!
HOW DOES IT WORK
- You will be liking other users' posts from your Instagram account
- You can select to either like or skip. If you don't want to do this manually, there's a switch that allows you to like all posts
- For each like you give you will get 1 heart
- You can exchange hearts to get likes from other users, 1 heart = 1 like
- Application allows you to select any of your posts on Instagram as long as your account is public


OUR FAIR USAGE POLICY
- The app will ask you to log in to your Instagram account, when you do that we will have no access to your login details
- The app will never attempt to like posts unless you give your permission
- The app will never attempt to publish comments or follow anyone from your account
- The app will not have access to your personal data
- The app will never attempt to get access to your account or change any of your settings


The application and its usage is free and we offer it "as is" without any guarantees.
